<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Health Products and Supplements</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/PandS.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="maincontainer">
        {{>navbar}}
        <header>
            <h1><span id="element"></span></h1>
        </header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="product" onclick="showProductDetails(1)">
                <h2>Multivitamins and Minerals</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>These are designed to provide a variety of essential vitamins and minerals that may be lacking
                        in
                        your diet.</li>
                    <li>
                        They can be beneficial if you have specific deficiencies or dietary restrictions.
                    </li>
                    <li>Consult a healthcare professional before taking multivitamins to ensure they're appropriate for
                        you.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="product" onclick="showProductDetails(2)">
                <h2>Omega-3 Fatty Acids</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Found in fish oil supplements, omega-3s are known for their potential cardiovascular and brain
                        health benefits.</li>
                    <li>They may help reduce inflammation and support heart health.</li>
                    <li>Consider consulting your doctor if you're interested in taking fish oil supplements.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="product" onclick="showProductDetails(3)">
                <h2>Vitamin D</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Vitamin D is essential for bone health, immune function, and overall well-being.</li>
                    <li>Some people, especially those with limited sun exposure, may require supplementation.</li>
                    <li>Your doctor can determine if you have a deficiency and recommend the appropriate dosage.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="product" onclick="showProductDetails(4)">
                <h2>Probiotics</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Probiotics contain beneficial bacteria that can support gut health and digestion.
                    </li>
                    <li>They may be helpful after taking antibiotics or for managing certain gastrointestinal issues.
                    </li>
                    <li>Consult a healthcare provider before using probiotics, especially if you have underlying health
                        conditions.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="product" onclick="showProductDetails(5)">
                <h2>Protein Supplements</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Protein supplements like whey, casein, and plant-based options are often used by athletes and
                        individuals looking to meet their protein needs.</li>
                    <li>They can be useful when it's challenging to consume enough protein through whole foods.</li>
                    <li>Consider your dietary goals and consult a dietitian if you're considering protein supplements.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="product" onclick="showProductDetails(6)">
                <h2>Creatine</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Creatine is popular among athletes and bodybuilders to support muscle performance and growth.
                    </li>
                    <li>It may enhance short-term high-intensity activities like weightlifting.</li>
                    <li>Consult your healthcare professional before using creatine, especially if you have kidney
                        issues.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="product" onclick="showProductDetails(7)">
                <h2>Green Tea Extract</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Green tea extract contains antioxidants called catechins that may offer potential health
                        benefits.
                    </li>
                    <li>Some studies suggest it could aid in weight management and provide cardiovascular support.</li>
                    <li>Be cautious about dosage, and consult your doctor before using green tea extract supplements.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="product" onclick="showProductDetails(8)">
                <h2>Melatonin</h2>
                <p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Melatonin is a hormone that regulates sleep-wake cycles.</li>
                    <li>It's commonly used as a supplement to address sleep disturbances and jet lag.</li>
                    <li>Consult a healthcare provider before using melatonin, especially if you have underlying health
                        conditions.</li>
                </ul>
                </p>
            </div>
            <!-- Add more products as needed -->
        </div>
        {{>footer}}
    </div>

